list.name: openingh.nvim
list.desc: ![GitHub Repo stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/almo7aya/openingh.nvim?color=%239f7b3d&style=flat-square): neovim plugin that gives you two simple commands `:OpenInGHRepo` and `:OpenInGHFile` to easily open the current file or repo page in GitHub.
